quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,Indeed We sent it down on the Night of Ordainment
  97,2,And what will show you what is the Night of Ordainment
  97,3,The Night of Ordainment is better than a thousand months
  97,4,"In it the angels and the Spirit descend, by the leave of their Lord, with every command"
  97,5,It is peaceful until the rising of the dawn